(30228, 'RPG Maker XP', 2004, 'RPG MAKER lets you create an original role-playing game without any prior specialized knowledge or training. RPG MAKER XP is full of the functions you`ve been asking for, including game data encryption and a scripting feature that lets you change the very heart of the RPG MAKER engine.  
 
