(33430, 'Cubicolor', 2016, 'Cubicolor is a minimalist puzzle game. The rules are simple: Match the color patches on the board and reach the exit, all on one single path. The game gets harder as the levels progress, always accompanying you with soothing piano tunes.', null, null),

(33451, 'Zombie Training Simulator', 2016, 'Are you ready for the zombie apocalypse? We`ve done the research and want to make sure you`re prepared. When the news reports the zombies are here and your friend gives you a call, "They`re here. I need you," how will you respond? 
 
That`s right, you`ll say "I`ll be right over. We`ve got this thanks to ZTS!"', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/m3x2zocvfihuyzqtmiqj.jpg', 8682),

(33414, 'Blast Brawl 2: Bloody Boogaloo', 2016, 'A fast-paced fighting game where any hit means DEATH! Battle your friends as a vastly diverse selection of characters, experiencing intense combat where every blow earns a kill, and skill reigns supreme. And what`s victory without a little dance?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1upd.jpg', null),

(33441, 'Sophie`s Curse', 2016, 'You got a job, which is to take care of an old man during the night in a recently purchased house; this house does not have electricity and you have to rely on some kind of hand crank generators to light the place up, but there is something in the darkness draining their power, don’t let it happen!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/gloye7bqnwljea1z9itf.jpg', null),

(33003, 'Predynastic Egypt', 2016, 'Turn-based historical simulation strategy will lead you through the history of Predynastic Egypt. Starting from 5000 B.C. you will guide the nomadic and humble Egyptian tribe through all the hardships to prosperity and power culminating in the Unification of Lower and Upper Egypt.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1mlg.jpg', 11268),

(33058, 'The Leisure of Grisaia', 2015, 'This side story to "The Fruit of Grisaia" is a character-driven visual novel featuring some of the same characters. This time, it`s Michiru who takes the lead role in this slapstick comedy. A laugh-out-loud side story detailing the Mihama girls` school hijinks.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27uz.jpg', 3032),

(33132, 'Forgotten, Not Lost - A Kinetic Novel', 2016, 'An old farmer lives with his wife - However, he hasn`t quite been himself lately. His mind wanders off, he forgets his daily routine and he often brings up things from the past. 

