(33913, 'Racket: Nx', 2017, 'Racket: Nx is an Arcade Space Sport, focusing on spatial awareness, motor control and reflexes. It`s inspired by Racquet-ball, classic arcade games, outer space, psychedelia, and competitive eSports.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24pu.jpg', null),

(33528, 'Sonicomi', 2016, 'Super Sonico is a cheerful, hardworking college student and amateur musician who`s about to make her modeling debut. As her personal photographer, you will be responsible for Sonico`s image, balancing the needs of your clients with your own vision for Sonico`s future. Cute, sexy, weird -- the costumes you choose will determine her path as a model. Will you cultivate mainstream appeal? Make Sonico a subculture icon? Or will she become something even you can`t imagine? It all depends on you! 
 
