-Your choices matter – 18 different endings to unlock.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2b7y.jpg', 3020),

(33501, 'Bloons TD Battles', 2016, 'Go head to head with other players in a Bloon-popping battle for victory. From the creators of best-selling Bloons TD 5, this all new Battles game is specially designed for multiplayer combat, featuring the ability to control bloons directly and send them charging past your opponent`s defenses.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1n4l.jpg', 8810),

(33572, 'Niche - a genetics survival game', 2016, 'Niche - a genetics survival game is a turn-based strategy game combined with simulation and roguelike elements. Shape your own species of animals based on real genetics. Keep your species alive against all odds, such as predators, climate change and spreading sickness.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1u0r.jpg', 13668),

(33558, 'Risky Rescue', 2016, 'Risky Rescue is a demanding arcade game with flat design graphics and innovative controls. Fly a helicopter and do dangerous missions rescuing people.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1zeh.jpg', 4741),

(33897, 'Cosmic Trip', 2016, 'Built exclusively for VR, Cosmic Trip is an award-winning real-time strategy game for the HTC Vive and Oculus Rift. Experience what it’s like to command an army of badass robots and fight against hostile enemies on beautiful alien planets.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23mx.jpg', 6557),

(33672, 'Prison Run and Gun', 2016, 'The recent events in a state prison, involving Jake from Hot Guns Team was a perfect moment for some prisoners to escape - you are one of them.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/lpgugrqjgftlnd88k6ql.jpg', 12674),

(33886, 'Red Haze', 2017, 'You know, my dear, it isn`t safe... To wander and creep while oh so weak. In the abandoned, the rotten, the decayed. Society has forgotten you; it won`t lift a finger for that which is tossed away. You`re just prey that the true prowlers who lay in shadows await to feast upon.', null, null),

(33613, 'Surfingers', 2016, 'Surf as far as you can. Through the oceans, caves, snowy hills and deserts full of sand.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/dbstxdlqhjsxkgvmkulu.jpg', 4741),

(33711, 'Moonlight', 2016, 'Moonlight is a short game, about a little character named Kinubo and his quest to the moon! Kinubo finds himself in a new village while looking for help on his quest, but most don`t accept his presence. The characters here are a very tight bunch, and they don`t take kindly to strangers! You must earn their acceptance, and the only way you`ll ever make it to the moon, is to win them over one by one!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co281z.jpg', null),

(33733, 'Bit Blaster XL', 2016, 'A throwback to the classic quarter eating arcade games of the 80`s. Bit Blaster XL is a retro styled, addictive, and fast paced arcade shoot `em up! (shmup).', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1o81.jpg', 15119),

(33838, 'WolfQuest', 2016, 'LIVE THE LIFE OF A WILD WOLF! WolfQuest is a wildlife simulation game about wolf ecology. Playing as a two-year-old gray wolf in Yellowstone National Park, you`ll learn how to live on your own, finding food, meeting other wolves, and searching for a mate. Ultimately, your goal is to find a home and raise your own family.

