Unlock new costumes for your pug and new characters to play as. 
Please try not to squish your pug!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/c2ktswnwluakqnebtarm.jpg', 8031),

(34259, 'SHOWTIME 2073', 2016, 'The best  shooter SHOW in 2073.Explosive, Fun & full destructive !', null, null),

(34293, 'BioShock Remastered', 2016, 'BioShock is a shooter unlike any other, loaded with unique weapons and tactics. Complete with an arsenal of revolvers, shotguns, and grenade launchers, players will be forced to genetically modify their DNA to become an even deadlier weapon.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1qq8.jpg', 8),

(34021, 'CHKN', 2016, 'Behold, the miracle of life… packed into cubes! Create fantastic creatures in an open-world sandbox game like no other. Explore, craft, and survive—all with the help of your very own creations.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/canbn4prytqycwclv7jk.jpg', null),

(34331, 'UniBall', 2017, 'One of the longest running independent games on the Internet, UniBall has evolved from a simple version of space hockey into an online multiplayer e-sport that is uniquely its own.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ks4mtg8qasosk95zaosg.jpg', null),

(34827, 'Asphyxia', 2015, 'Samantha and Lillian are best friends. At least, they were, until everything fell apart. Now, Samantha has a day to repair their relationship – but is it already too late?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/owf0rl9fsy7ulawnl0en.jpg', 5325),

(34737, 'Braveland Pirate', 2015, 'The Braveland trilogy concludes with the most exciting book of all, number three – welcome to Braveland Pirate strategy game! A crew of pirates led by Captain Jim embarks on a search for the Eternal Treasure.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21sf.jpg', 4696),

(34808, 'DungeonUp', 2015, 'A challenging rogue-like puzzler inspired by the classic Tower of the Sorcerer. Play as a human knight who fights his way out of a deep dungeon by slaying monsters and solving intricate puzzles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co213u.jpg', 9147),

(34935, 'Dungeon Nightmares II: The Memory', 2015, 'Dungeon Nightmares II is a first-person psychological horror that takes you through a journey of discovering what nightmares are.

The game is inspired by classic roguelike games which include 100% procedural-generated maps and permadeath. These features play an important part in making this game tense with the feeling of dread & terror as you walk the hallways of the dungeon.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2d3h.jpg', null),

(34531, 'Without Within 2', 2015, 'Vinty is back as she travels to Melbourne in hopes of meeting her calligraphy idol. Excelia. Determined to study and mimic the star`s every move, will Vinty end up losing her identity?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1o2c.jpg', 21490),

(34594, 'Shmadow', 2015, 'Inspired by “shmups” and shadows, Shmadow is a modern twin-stick side-scroller that nods to retro arcade gameplay. Use your light to blast through your enemies, unlock new powers, and defeat bosses before the darkness extinguishes you.', null, 13735),

(34644, 'Square Brawl', 2015, 'A fast and skill based party game where all of the focus lies in fun and engaging gameplay.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ngm.jpg', 9453),

(34579, 'A Wise Use of Time', 2015, 'With the power to freeze time, you can ransack a casino, rescue a celebrity, or cheat death itself! A thrilling interactive sci-fi novel.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/abqecgaujmqjfejehcob.jpg', 16347),

(34939, 'Eco', 2018, 'Eco is an online global-survival world from Strange Loop Games, where players must build civilization using resources from an ecosystem that can be damaged and destroyed. The world of Eco is an incredibly reactive one, and whatever any player does in the world affects the underlying ecosystem. As a group you can make laws regarding the world, in order to protect its sensitive ecosystem. The game can also be played offline, if the player prefers to do so.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wlv.jpg', 4373),

(34656, 'Rot Gut', 2016, 'Rot Gut is an action packed platformer set in America’s 1920’s Prohibition era. You take control of an agent who, to uncover their mysteries, goes on a mission to fight the city’s underground armed to the teeth organizations.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/b8cxmxwu1gofw45lqwsz.jpg', null),

(34697, 'New York Mysteries: High Voltage', 2016, 'Fearless journalist Laura is again brought in to investigate strange murders taking place in New York. Immerse yourself in an exciting crime story and solve the mystery of a dangerous criminal surrounded by lightning!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/nwlwwidq88vxrkuhikio.jpg', 13358),

